  - elementId: gap-text
    elementType: text
    bounds: [80, 530, 1120, 80]
    content:
      style: "$body"
      align: [left, top]
      text: |
        <p><strong>Identified Gap</strong></p>
        <p style="margin-top:4px">No existing method simultaneously achieves: (i) sub-quadratic complexity, (ii) end-to-end differentiability, (iii) explicit multi-resolution structure matching document hierarchy, and (iv) strong empirical performance across diverse long-document tasks. HSA addresses all four criteria.</p>

